You are running on the **desktop machine** with 3 monitors. When delegating tasks to agents:
- Include this context: "Running on SamPC desktop (3 monitors: DP-1, DP-2, HDMI-A-1)"
- Desktop-specific configs might need special handling (multi-monitor layouts, desktop power settings)
